WEBVTT

00:00:06.324 --> 00:00:08.424
She'll be here soon.

00:00:14.864 --> 00:00:17.404
What's going on with you and Stella...

00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:22.320
What is she like?

00:00:29.237 --> 00:00:30.976
Bottoms up.

00:00:47.722 --> 00:00:49.822
Are you two close?

00:00:51.835 --> 00:00:53.765
Stella is...

00:01:01.562 --> 00:01:03.662
Is Stella...

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:20.840
Are we really doing this?

00:01:20.840 --> 00:01:22.200
Who cares?

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:23.413
You do it, then.

00:01:23.413 --> 00:01:25.130
- Me?
- Yeah.

00:01:26.100 --> 00:01:28.033
He's here, he's here.

00:01:36.554 --> 00:01:38.654
Well, Hyun Jae...

00:01:40.201 --> 00:01:42.141
Let's take a choreo video.

00:01:42.141 --> 00:01:44.241
Let's do it, come on.

00:01:49.568 --> 00:01:51.263
Soo An!

00:01:52.208 --> 00:01:54.955
Let's do a choreo video with these guys.

00:01:56.654 --> 00:01:58.754
Come on, let's do it!

00:01:59.870 --> 00:02:01.970
Just this once, okay?

00:02:24.254 --> 00:02:26.934
Wow, who would've thought this would blow up?

00:02:26.934 --> 00:02:28.101
How many views, again?

00:02:28.101 --> 00:02:29.578
Over 18 million now.

00:02:29.578 --> 00:02:31.254
18 million, huh?

00:02:31.254 --> 00:02:34.627
Okay.
We can't let this opportunity go to waste.

00:02:34.627 --> 00:02:36.011
Hyun Jae, Soo An!

00:02:36.011 --> 00:02:37.241
- Yes, sir?
- Yes?

00:02:37.241 --> 00:02:39.874
- Do another one together.
- Yes, sir.

00:02:39.874 --> 00:02:40.874
Huh?

00:02:40.874 --> 00:02:42.857
We should keep it going.

00:02:42.857 --> 00:02:45.724
Exactly. The fans want to see the two of you.

00:02:45.724 --> 00:02:47.530
So we'll shoot some videos with just you two.

00:02:47.530 --> 00:02:50.144
For the making-of video,
why don't you two do it together?

00:02:50.144 --> 00:02:53.603
- What do you think?
- Yes, sir. We'll do our best.

00:02:55.110 --> 00:02:56.775
Yes, sir.

00:03:00.197 --> 00:03:02.277
Got any ideas?

00:03:02.277 --> 00:03:03.991
I don't know.

00:03:05.617 --> 00:03:07.843
Maybe we should have a meeting first?

00:03:07.843 --> 00:03:09.862
Let's take things slow.

00:03:10.810 --> 00:03:12.727
Hey, Ha Jun!

00:03:34.917 --> 00:03:37.923
Ugh, this place again.

00:03:40.004 --> 00:03:44.196
Shin Jae Min, you idiot.

00:03:46.344 --> 00:03:48.237
Hold on!

00:03:48.237 --> 00:03:49.637
Don't come in yet!

00:03:49.637 --> 00:03:51.990
Don't come in. I mean it!

00:03:56.484 --> 00:03:57.863
Huh?

00:03:59.450 --> 00:04:02.004
Relax.

00:04:02.004 --> 00:04:04.297
It's just breakfast.

00:04:10.204 --> 00:04:12.930
You don't need to be scared of me.

00:04:12.930 --> 00:04:15.024
No, it's not that.

00:04:15.024 --> 00:04:17.542
It's just kind of awkward, you see.

00:04:18.490 --> 00:04:20.150
Understandable.

00:04:20.150 --> 00:04:22.750
You didn't expect to see me here, right?

00:04:22.750 --> 00:04:24.417
Of course not.

00:04:24.417 --> 00:04:26.570
I didn't expect to wake up here, either.

00:04:26.570 --> 00:04:29.250
Breakfast was even more of a surprise.

00:04:30.370 --> 00:04:32.564
Khun asked me to.

00:04:32.564 --> 00:04:36.368
He said,
"Make sure Jae Min gets his breakfast."

00:04:37.764 --> 00:04:40.379
Khun. He's nice, isn't he?

00:04:41.317 --> 00:04:42.824
Then...

00:04:42.824 --> 00:04:44.370
Where is he right now?

00:04:44.370 --> 00:04:46.690
At the language school.

00:04:46.690 --> 00:04:49.149
He's studying Korean there.

00:04:50.370 --> 00:04:52.224
He's been studying pretty hard.

00:04:52.224 --> 00:04:56.528
Perhaps because he wants to
talk to you more freely, I wonder?

00:05:03.966 --> 00:05:05.358
Khun...

00:05:05.358 --> 00:05:08.117
was pretty popular in Thailand.

00:05:08.950 --> 00:05:10.154
Big stage,

00:05:10.154 --> 00:05:11.570
lots of fans,

00:05:11.570 --> 00:05:13.030
TV shows...

00:05:13.030 --> 00:05:15.737
CFs, everything.

00:05:16.604 --> 00:05:20.405
I was his friend,
and a manager at a Thai company.

00:05:22.117 --> 00:05:24.537
He's been through a lot.

00:05:24.537 --> 00:05:27.159
He's had lots of heartbreaks, too.

00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:30.990
Is that why he came here?

00:05:30.990 --> 00:05:32.499
All by himself?

00:05:32.499 --> 00:05:34.506
Maybe to breathe?

00:05:35.137 --> 00:05:38.096
Or... to escape.

00:05:38.977 --> 00:05:42.290
But, ever since he met you, Jae Min,

00:05:42.290 --> 00:05:45.016
he's changed a lot.

00:05:48.124 --> 00:05:50.430
Khun...

00:05:50.430 --> 00:05:52.377
You like him, right?

00:05:56.690 --> 00:05:58.348
Sorry.

00:05:58.942 --> 00:06:01.797
But I had to ask.

00:06:01.797 --> 00:06:04.924
You look like someone
who doesn't know how obvious he is.

00:06:04.924 --> 00:06:07.917
No, it's not like that. It's just...

00:06:07.917 --> 00:06:10.010
Well, I'm worried about him.

00:06:10.010 --> 00:06:11.830
As anyone should.

00:06:12.877 --> 00:06:14.764
Okay.

00:06:14.764 --> 00:06:16.915
As anyone should, huh?

00:06:18.130 --> 00:06:20.025
However...

00:06:20.850 --> 00:06:23.795
I mean it when I say this.

00:06:24.670 --> 00:06:28.350
Khun is fragile.

00:06:28.350 --> 00:06:31.184
More than he lets it show.

00:06:31.184 --> 00:06:33.852
And you, Jae Min...

00:06:33.852 --> 00:06:36.606
seems to be quite special to him.

00:06:37.897 --> 00:06:41.930
So, be good to him.

00:06:41.930 --> 00:06:43.842
Please.

00:07:02.505 --> 00:07:05.223
How about we shoot a Reels video as a pair?

00:07:07.230 --> 00:07:10.402
I was in the middle of practice.
Ha Jun must be waiting for me.

00:07:17.729 --> 00:07:19.690
How about we talk over some food?

00:07:19.690 --> 00:07:21.720
I'll think about it.

00:07:28.017 --> 00:07:30.203
Oh, Soo An!

00:07:30.203 --> 00:07:32.143
What a coincidence.

00:07:32.143 --> 00:07:34.463
- How about that talk?
- My vocal teacher is waiting for me.

00:07:34.463 --> 00:07:36.416
I'll catch you later.

00:08:08.403 --> 00:08:10.081
Jae Min.

00:08:12.903 --> 00:08:14.770
Hello.

00:08:14.770 --> 00:08:16.971
I'm Shin Jae Min.

00:08:20.763 --> 00:08:23.170
Why is he so drunk?

00:08:25.803 --> 00:08:29.281
He's got a low tolerance.

00:08:30.117 --> 00:08:32.010
Cute.

00:08:35.098 --> 00:08:37.482
I'm not cute at all.

00:08:42.937 --> 00:08:46.570
How's your language class going?

00:08:46.570 --> 00:08:48.377
Did you get better at Korean?

00:08:48.377 --> 00:08:50.690
Yeah, way better.

00:08:50.690 --> 00:08:52.644
Damn good, actually.

00:08:53.497 --> 00:08:56.850
Wow, you really are good at it.

00:08:56.850 --> 00:08:58.470
What do you think?

00:08:58.470 --> 00:09:02.053
You're just... amazing.

00:09:08.303 --> 00:09:10.403
You two look good...

00:09:13.703 --> 00:09:16.541
No, you don't look good together at all.

00:09:19.684 --> 00:09:22.668
You two are silly in the same way.

00:09:35.355 --> 00:09:37.308
This is delicious.

00:09:37.308 --> 00:09:39.548
No...

00:09:39.548 --> 00:09:42.268
Not delicious at all.

00:09:47.741 --> 00:09:51.295
I never thought you'd jump back in.

00:09:52.548 --> 00:09:54.920
I guess it's because of him.

00:10:02.421 --> 00:10:03.715
Stayed out again?

00:10:03.715 --> 00:10:06.248
And you're here again.

00:10:06.248 --> 00:10:08.248
Seriously, who are you seeing?

00:10:08.248 --> 00:10:09.812
You two should live together at this point.

00:10:09.812 --> 00:10:11.200
It's not like that.

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:14.433
- Nonsense.
- I'm serious!

00:10:15.113 --> 00:10:16.487
Hey.

00:10:16.487 --> 00:10:17.860
Who is it?

00:10:17.860 --> 00:10:20.872
- Tell me.
- Stop it.

00:10:30.220 --> 00:10:32.040
Hey.

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:35.647
What are you hesitating for?
The answer is clear.

00:10:35.647 --> 00:10:36.827
Confess.

00:10:36.827 --> 00:10:38.927
Have you lost it?

00:10:40.960 --> 00:10:43.240
Never mind, then.

00:10:45.947 --> 00:10:47.739
Confess?

00:10:48.820 --> 00:10:50.509
Confess?

00:10:52.967 --> 00:10:54.197
Hi, everyone!

00:10:54.197 --> 00:10:55.980
It's been a while.

00:10:55.980 --> 00:10:58.740
We saw how much you liked
our last choreography video.

00:10:58.740 --> 00:11:00.368
So I'm doing this live as a thank you of sorts.

00:11:00.368 --> 00:11:02.230
[I'm not dreaming, am I?]
[Didn't even have time to breathe!]

00:11:02.230 --> 00:11:03.273
[Where is this?]

00:11:03.273 --> 00:11:05.533
[You look even better! How do you do it?]
And...

00:11:05.533 --> 00:11:07.633
Ta-da!

00:11:08.660 --> 00:11:09.677
What?

00:11:09.677 --> 00:11:10.960
[Who's that?]
[No way!]

00:11:10.960 --> 00:11:13.756
Yoon Soo An, say hello to the fans.

00:11:13.756 --> 00:11:15.011
[Soo An?]
[It's Yoon Soo An!]

00:11:18.443 --> 00:11:20.127
[Am I dreaming? The Mallangs are so back!]

00:11:20.127 --> 00:11:22.120
[Mallangs!]
[Wow, the two of them together again?]

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:25.347
[It's been so long, Soo An...]
Hello, everyone. It's been a while.

00:11:25.347 --> 00:11:29.253
I've been doing wonderfully,
thanks to all your love and support.

00:11:29.253 --> 00:11:32.187
You guys showed us
so much love for our choreo video.

00:11:32.187 --> 00:11:34.320
So, we have a gift for you in the making.

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:37.373
[You two should be in the same group!]
It's going to be phenomenal, so stay tuned!

00:11:37.373 --> 00:11:38.865
Next week, coming soon!

00:11:38.865 --> 00:11:40.367
[I'll never sleep now!]
[Don't end the live!]

00:11:40.367 --> 00:11:42.493
See you again. Bye!

00:11:42.493 --> 00:11:43.844
[So pumped!]
[I can't wait!]

00:11:47.913 --> 00:11:49.376
Now we'll have to get ready fast.

00:11:49.376 --> 00:11:51.156
Don't you think?

00:12:03.460 --> 00:12:05.270
Good morning!

00:12:06.393 --> 00:12:08.493
Time to head to the shoot.

00:12:16.740 --> 00:12:19.387
But, are you okay?

00:12:20.867 --> 00:12:24.369
It won't be the same from now on.

00:12:41.010 --> 00:12:44.000
Just trust me and do what I say for today.

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:45.682
I've prepared everything.

00:12:45.682 --> 00:12:47.087
[To Khun]
I like you.

00:12:47.087 --> 00:12:48.513
Want to go here today?

00:12:48.513 --> 00:12:49.620
I've got things to do.

00:12:49.620 --> 00:12:52.197
- Then how about tomorrow?
- I'm busy.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:55.984
- Open wide.
- Remember the survival show?

00:12:55.984 --> 00:12:57.097
We used to...

00:12:57.097 --> 00:12:58.111
Open up.

00:12:58.111 --> 00:13:01.413
do all kinds of stuff in front of the camera.

00:13:01.413 --> 00:13:03.075
Everything I did then...

00:13:03.075 --> 00:13:05.270
I meant all of it.